Anonymous Wed 17 Nov 2021 05:26:12 No.43246730 Report
Quoted By:
>>43245630
It depends

I use two stages for larger projects
For me, there is a distinction between first readers and beta readers, much like alpha/beta in software
Firsts deal with nuts & bolts issues or development
Earlier betas might be about pacing opinions or seeing if you've got things squared away
A later beta should be polishing things up and getting the new story shine on the beast
